# evals-project — example environment.
# Copy to .env (gitignored) and fill in. Everything is optional: with no judge
# configured, judge() returns score=None and callers degrade gracefully.

# ── Where to POST status/eval results (optional; only if you use report()) ──
# REPORT_URL=https://your-app.example.com/api/report
# REPORT_SECRET=your-shared-secret        # sent as the x-report-secret header

# ── The judge (LLM-as-judge). Pick ONE provider. ─────────────────────────────
# judge() auto-selects: Anthropic if ANTHROPIC_API_KEY is set, else an
# OpenAI-compatible endpoint if EVAL_JUDGE_URL/KEY are set. Force one with
# EVAL_JUDGE_PROVIDER = "anthropic" | "openai".
#
# RIGOR: judge with a DIFFERENT model family than the one that produced the
# output, or self-preference bias inflates the score (knowledge-base/judge-biases.md).

# Option A — local Ollama (free, offline, easy cross-family judge). RECOMMENDED
# when your generator is a hosted model (Claude/GPT/Gemini): a local open model
# is a different family at zero cost. Ollama speaks the OpenAI chat API.
#   1. install ollama, then:  ollama pull qwen2.5:7b
#   2. ollama serve   (or just launch the app)
EVAL_JUDGE_PROVIDER=openai
EVAL_JUDGE_URL=http://localhost:11434/v1/chat/completions
EVAL_JUDGE_KEY=ollama          # Ollama ignores it, but the client requires a non-empty key
EVAL_JUDGE_MODEL=qwen2.5:7b

# Option B — a hosted OpenAI-compatible endpoint (OpenAI, Gemini's OpenAI
# endpoint, Groq, ...). Comment out Option A and use:
# EVAL_JUDGE_PROVIDER=openai
# EVAL_JUDGE_URL=https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/openai/chat/completions
# EVAL_JUDGE_KEY=your-gemini-key
# EVAL_JUDGE_MODEL=gemini-2.0-flash

# Option C — Anthropic native (only if your generator is NOT Claude).
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-anthropic-key
# EVAL_JUDGE_MODEL=claude-haiku-4-5-20251001

# ── Example data wiring (toolkit/examples/sync_dashboard.py) ──
# EVAL_DATA_DIR=.            # folder with predictions.jsonl, recaps/, latest-report.json
# EVAL_AGENT_ID=agent        # the id this agent reports under
